The Url shared in twitter along with a specified search term is instantly opened in the browser.
Helps in availing discounts and winning online contests where agility and speed is important.
Automates the quick link opening process
There are 2 versions ->
Polling - uses the refresh rate specified in config.ini
Streaming -> always connected using a socket. 
			adv 	-> REALTIME.
			disadv  -> AUTH required.


